*.log
.omc/
.host/
package-lock.json
storybook-static/
# Legacy binary lockfile from older bun versions; we standardize on text bun.lock.
bun.lockb
# dist/ is regenerated by `prepare` on every consumer `bun install`
# (tsup + tsc -p tsconfig.build.json). Committing it forced PRs to rebase
# their dist whenever main moved AND surfaced OS-specific tsc differences
# (.d.ts.map mappings differ between macOS and Linux). The fresh-build-on-
# install path eliminates both classes of CI churn at the cost of ~1-2s
# per consumer install.
dist/
